# Users API

Resources related to users

## User Collection [/api/users]

### List All Users [GET]
Roles: **[admin]**

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "_id": "5895adafa179991ac84e7793",
                "nickName": "azaliasz",
                "name": "admin",
                "email": "admin@a.pl",
