## User [/api/users/{user_id}]        
+ Parameters
    + user_id (String) - ID of the User in the form of an ObjectID
    

### Add New User [POST]
Roles: **[admin]**

+ Request (application/json)

        {
          "nickName": "testUser",
          "name": "test user",
          "email": "test@a.pl",
          "password": "secretHashedPassword",
          "projects" : [],
          "roles": [
            "user"
          ],
          "active": true
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "__v": 0,
          "_id": "589753f61f379020cabe634c",
          "nickName": "testUser",
          "name": "test user",
          "email": "ttttt@a.pl",
          "created_at": "2017-02-04T10:59:43.684Z",
          "updated_at": "2017-02-05T16:33:58.129Z",
          "roles": [
            "user"
          ],
          "active": true
        }
        
        
+ Response 500 (application/json)
    
        {
            "errorMsg": "Adding user failed"
        }

    
